        <p><strong>Diagnosis:</strong> Performed standard F01 diagnostic order. Step 1 reset (10-minute power cycle), F01 returned within 30 seconds of restart. Confirmed CCU failure. Pulled the model serial and confirmed the OEM Whirlpool CCU part number for this generation Cabrio.</p>
        <p><strong>Repair:</strong> Replaced the CCU with new OEM Whirlpool part. Verified all dryer functions through a complete cycle including heating, drum rotation, and panel response. Cleaned the vent run as part of the visit (lint trap was 60% clogged, unrelated to F01 but addressed proactively).</p>
        <p><strong>Cost &amp; time:</strong> $485 total. Two visits over 24 hours (parts on-truck for this generation; verification call required).</p>
